#Computer
#Telecommunication

==Lab facilities==
Institute of Information Technology Bogra (IITB)  has some of the best Privet Polytechnic  lab facilities in the country. The Electrical Lab, Electronics Labs & the Computer Lab are well-equipped and large in size. Facilities include two computer labs equipped with multimedia projectors, a separate internet lab, two advanced chemistry labs, two physics labs.

